OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FBreezy
OL,6,Fand cloudy, with outbreaks of rain
OL,7,FTuesday morning, followed by showers.
OL,8,FBlustery showers, with possible
OL,9,Fthunder, and some sunny intervals
OL,10,FWednesday and Thursday. Cool.
